'''Homam El-Amin Mohamed Ahmed''' ({{langx|ar|همام الأمين محمد أحمد}}; born 25 August 1999) is a [[Qatar]]i professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)#Full-back|left back]] for [[Cultural y Deportiva Leonesa|Cultural Leonesa]], on loan from [[Al-Duhail SC|Al-Duhail]] and the [[Qatar national football team|Qatar national team]].<ref>{{Soccerway|homam-ahmed-ahmed/465705|accessdate=1 June 2019}}</ref>

